originalText.text: I saw Dr. Ianzano today at Kurpis center today and he is beyond the most amazing dentist I’ve ever been to. Not only is he personable and professional. He’s an artist! My teeth look so amazing I wanted to cry tears of joy! Highly recommended!

originalText.text: I was treated by Dr. Kurpis at this office last year, and to follow up on my procedure and to improve the rest of the my dental issues, I've been seeing Dr. Ianzano for the last six to seven months. The office staff is still very professional, and Dr. Ianzano is a really great guy to talk to

originalText.text: Literally saved me from a life of pain and suffering. Was honest and straight forward about what to expect.  Saved a tooth that would have been easier to extract and substitute with an implant. I am very grateful. Eileen in reception and Danielle were cheerful.
